<area shape="rect" id="node1" title="dsgrid.config.mapping_tables.MappingTableByNameModel

Attributes for a dimension mapping table for soon&#45;to&#45;be registered dimensions by name.
This will be converted to a MappingTableModel as soon as the dimensions are registered.

Attributes:
 &#160;&#160;&#160;mapping_type (DimensionMappingType(DSGEnum)): Type/purpose of the dimension mapping. Default is &#39;many_to_one_aggregation&#39;.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;archetype (Optional[DimensionMappingArchetype(DSGEnum)]): Dimension mapping archetype, determined based on mapping_type. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;description (str): Description of dimension mapping
 &#160;&#160;&#160;from_fraction_tolerance (Optional[float]): Tolerance value to apply to the from_fraction column. Default is 1e&#45;09.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;to_fraction_tolerance (Optional[float]): Tolerance value to apply to the to_fraction column. Default is 1e&#45;09.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;filename (str): Filename containing association table records.
